{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 169716, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "蹲", "timestamp": 1595581398, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 169731, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "水…利？", "timestamp": 1595581455, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 169744, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不招本科生", "timestamp": 1595581574, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 169747, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "系的名字叫地学系，以前有辅修现在也没了", "timestamp": 1595581608, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 169749, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 这样啊", "timestamp": 1595581616, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 169772, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "去北大吧，北大地空学院多好", "timestamp": 1595581911, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 169834, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "小孩子根本不懂那些专业是什么意思", "timestamp": 1595582736, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 169836, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你就问他以后一个月想赚多少钱就好了", "timestamp": 1595582750, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 169853, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 水利的培养方案和地质差别很大吧？", "timestamp": 1595582973, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 169867, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 清华地学是地球系统科学系，不招本科生，研究生（基本都是博士了）包括生态学和大气科学两个学位，以气候变化、大气海洋为主，地质的老师好像不多（可以去官网上看一下）。印象中有对地震进行数值模拟的。", "timestamp": 1595583263, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 169893, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果想研究生去地学系，本科选哪个专业比较接近？", "timestamp": 1595583731, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 170030, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 他们家都是搞石油的，他爸妈想让他进国企", "timestamp": 1595585774, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 170199, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "水利只有工程地质稍微沾边，还是隔壁吧", "timestamp": 1595588280, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 170254, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 貌似没有太接近的 清华没有任何院系会开设大气物理、天气学这类专业基础课课程，只有隔壁有。\n环境、水利会有一点点相关课程，比如流体力学、海洋学、卫星遥感。\n所以本校基本都是跨转。数理基础或编程能力会有优势。有些关注全球气候变化的老师会喜欢经济学背景的学生。", "timestamp": 1595588918, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2962849, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 30129, "reply_to": 170030, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 地学系有个老师做勘探地球物理，和石油公司有合作", "timestamp": 1637124365, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 30129, "reply": 15, "tag": null, "text": "咱们学校有地质系吗，我亲戚孩子想学地质是不是只能去隔壁了。", "timestamp": 1595581283, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1637124366, "url": "", "vote": {}}}